Holmes was dripping of sweat and his pupils were wildly dilated as he told the officer that his apartment had been booby trapped.

Officer Justin Grizzle testified that Holmes had a 'smirk' on his face as the carnage unfolded around him.

Fighting back tears, Officer Grizzle recalled today how he saw 'several' bodies - and slipped on blood that was on the floor as he entered the theater.

