of the moving patrol car.

He said there was so much blood in his car that he could hear it sloshing around.

A third officer, Aaron Blue, recalled 
arriving on the scene to find 'a lot of people coming out of the theater
screaming,' and testified about how he and his partner transported one 
woman to the hospital as he sat in the back seat cradling her head.

